flowchart LR
    User[Support Engineer / Admin] --> Internet[Internet]
    Internet --> AWSVPC[AWS VPC]
    Internet --> AzureVNet[Azure VNet]

    subgraph AWS[AWS Environment]
        AWSVPC --> AWSPublic[Public Subnet]
        AWSVPC --> AWSPrivate[Private Subnet]
        AWSPublic --> EC2[EC2 Test Instance]
        AWSPrivate --> S3[S3 Storage]
        IAM[AWS IAM Roles & Policies] --> EC2
        IAM --> S3
        SG[Security Groups] --> EC2
    end

    subgraph AZURE[Azure Environment]
        AzureVNet --> AzurePublic[App Subnet]
        AzureVNet --> AzurePrivate[Data Subnet]
        AzurePublic --> VM[Azure VM]
        AzurePrivate --> Blob[Azure Blob Storage]
        Entra[Microsoft Entra ID / RBAC] --> VM
        Entra --> Blob
        NSG[Network Security Groups] --> VM
    end

    EC2 --> Monitoring[CloudWatch / Azure Monitor / Grafana]
    VM --> Monitoring
    S3 --> Backup[Backup & DR Plan]
    Blob --> Backup
